      "file_path": "docs/sections/services/pm-mapper/configuration.rst",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 36,
      "message": "Another good chance to fix this a little,\nI'd probably say something like:\n\nList of Strings or Regular expressions\n\n\nList is generally easier to understand as a concept than an array, and reads better to someone who doesn't know the CS definitions of either :)",
      "author": {
